  "text": "Secondly, we applied the BCJ amplitude relations [CITATION_1] to relate all non-planar generalized unitarity cuts to the previously computed planar ones. This allowed us to easily generate a compact representation the full colour two-loop, five-gluon, all-plus integrand building on previous planar work [CITATION_2] . The soft infrared poles of the full amplitude were checked against the well-known universal pole structure.",
